Title: Legend (2)
Plot: With the appearance of Mossad agent Michael Rivkin, Tony is forced to question Ziva's loyalty to NCIS. Meanwhile, in Los Angeles, Special Agent Callen goes undercover to try to catch a terrorist cell while OSP psychologist Nate Getz discovers the startling truth about Gibbs and Special Agent Lara Macy's relationship.
GuestStars: Nick Tarabay, Peter Cambor, Merik Tadros, Brian Avers, Barrett Foa, LL Cool J, Louise Lombard, Chris O'Donnell, Daniela Ruah, Dilshad Vadsaria
